-- Valeant sees 'unrivaled' growth in possible Allergan merger
-- 
-- Mon Apr 21, 2014 05:36PM EDT
-- None



April 21 (Reuters) - A merger between Valeant Pharmaceuticals International Inc <VRX.TO> and Allergan Inc <AGN.N> would create an "unrivaled platform for growth and value creation" in the healthcare sector, a spokesperson for Valeant said on Monday.

